{"type": "article", "id": 49846, "title": "你了解修复碎瓷器的工艺吗？这里有个艺术版本｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-02-01T23:16:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 18311, "name": "Native Union"}, {"id": 47514, "name": "Mattiazzi"}, {"id": 47515, "name": "Pedrali"}, {"id": 26039, "name": "Seletti"}, {"id": 47516, "name": "Kauppi & Kauppi"}, {"id": 23568, "name": "Konstantin Grcic"}, {"id": 29036, "name": "Stelios Mousarris"}, {"id": 19982, "name": "Patrick Norguet"}, {"id": 47517, "name": "Marcantonio"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 12, "praise_count": 76, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180202071549LUEvR6z91X2Vy374.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Limbus Greenframe by Kauppi &amp; Kauppi</h3><p>Limbus Greenframe 是一款简洁木制框架，由白蜡木制作而成，经过计算机数控切割，灯源、电线以及适配器均被隐藏在木框之中。植物托盘与木腿在框架底部用螺丝固定，一条带着脚踏开关的长绳用来控制电灯开关。绿植木架由两个小支柱支撑，可做台灯和植物架，还可以做空间分割的屏风。</p><p>设计师 Johan Kauppi 说：“我希望探索出一个屏风设计究竟可以简化为何种程度。当所有人都在希望减少空木架的结构，我却开始对用什么东西将其填满更加感兴趣。我非常希望我的办公桌附近有一片森林，里面是漂亮的松树，这会让我感到开心。”</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180201190653eKnTpbdasgiCkjoO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180201190653Y4RHfVp5cBmD7MeT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.593519\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180201190654suVOTUtqP72AeI9E.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.399756\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180201190654wdHyubiGNolADTK1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180201190655ktYcuB8GvaxzrF16.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201802011906550fiHLZqIyToMwjx4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.713936\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180201190655oxaeO0kPDMQWpt8z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.713936\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Kintsugi Collection by Marcantonio for Seletti</h3><p>意大利设计品牌 Seletti 推出了最新系列 Kintsugi，掌舵这个系列的是意大利设计师 Marcantonio。据称其灵感来自数百年前日本出现的一种名为金繕（Kintsugi ）的传统工艺，利用漆料与金粉混合，对破碎的瓷器进行修复。</p><p>在 Kintsugi 系列中，Marcantonio 将修复感进一步加重，利用 24K 纯金脉络将破碎的瓷片重新粘连在一起，最终制成了由多种色彩和形状组成的独一无二的全新餐具作品。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180201190728nAwzhkoqSP0W4TOm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.800733\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180201190729WnDURzYF3uTK4HdL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333741\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180201190729chRGgOeN3DS7BjMX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333741\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180201190729l4FmbJT1wVKv6gES.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.361111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180201190729OqdmEkyaAVHDiUI2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250611\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Fox Armchair by Patrick Norguet for Pedrali</h3><p>这款造型优雅的扶手椅，是意大利家具公司 Pedrali 邀请设计师 Patrick Norguet 设计的。扶手椅采用了一系列混合材料以及对比性极强的几何线条。椅子的外壳用纤细的玻璃丝来加固聚丙烯，再与白蜡木相结合，经过雕刻实现圆边处理，就好像一个张开怀抱给人们以温暖的拥抱欢迎礼。此外，Fox 扶手椅还具备可折叠的特点。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180201190759F6IoaKANVHlfTZik.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.913203\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180201190801HaJgIxSyLUzCAWB6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.361111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180201190801U0QhPWyo2pzldHbJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.949878\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180201190802wCyIUv65LZFQseGf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.019560\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>City Pendant Light by Stelios Mousarris</h3><p>我们之前曾介绍过塞浦路斯设计师 Stelios Mousarris 设计的 Wave City 咖啡桌与餐桌，最近他又推出了一款城市吊灯。这一次设计师将城市场景弯曲成环形，并从内部点亮。这款吊灯线条纤细，哑光黑色表面，暗黑系气质，充满暗影、图案以及荒凉的明暗对比。坚固的钢制骨架，将设计者创造的虚构天际线稳稳固定在适当位置。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180201190907axYoIMEy924Ch08H.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562347\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180201190907s8TZdUg3z5m9Hpcj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562347\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180201190907tABrSu37OnzFQqYc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562347\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201802011909087MaqlSr8WeuDv5FE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562347\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180201190908F7ehPadUL2iVwcr4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.361111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Primo Collection by Konstantin Grcic for Mattiazzi</h3><p>意大利木质家具公司 Mattiazzi 邀请慕尼黑设计师 Konstantin Grcic，联手推出了最新系列 Primo。在这个系列中，他参考经典椅子的形态，对其进行极简化处理，精简到仅剩四条椅腿、一个座面和靠背的最基本元素，通过座椅腿严格垂直的方向创造出强烈的建筑风格。</p><p>设计师特意将靠背设计成弯曲形态，创造出靠背悬浮在座椅后侧顶端的效果。Primo 系列运用榉木制作，包含一款座椅、一款高脚凳和一款桌子，提供黑色漆面、金色和橡木色三种饰面选择。整个系列座椅均可堆叠，桌子腿可拆卸，以节省运输空间。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180201190934BEAKwYSDN5Xtrp8O.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180201190934O1AeJ8gRGzfZCKoM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.749389\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201802011909349toMY8mxeqHuQbLc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.812958\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201802011909340yQhU2CveEfD4oLZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.128362\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180201190934TqnBXN927hWrwJja.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.014670\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201802011909349a6B4q5HWKELrtu1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.361111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180201190935gyOK0uTPeGda8Fi4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.894866\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Native Union Drop by Native Union</h3><p>Native Union 是香港一家配件品牌，最近推出了名为 Native Union Drop 的无线充电器，先后在 CES 展会和巴黎家居装饰博览会上亮相。Native Union 一贯以来的优势，就是擅长处理美学和功能性的平衡。</p><p>这款无线充电器便是采用了航空级铝材基座，纺织面料外层贴覆着硅胶胎面，防止过热的同时也能保持安全性。它适配于任何无线充电标准的设备，包括 iPhone 8，iPhone 8 Plus，iPhone X 等，并配有一个集成皮带，用于包裹缆线，既可以调整长度，又可以方便收纳。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180201191000sSbVNH7dP402rYwg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180201191001i84Krmb9IVEjMf1S.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180201191003M2peQdsmc6IKqkDo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180201191002FYq12u3S0lzWDHRA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180201191003GvLRTBSNp5YU93my.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201802011910037k2RF5EBZOAGwo91.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}